message.body: Hi! I didn't get a chance to wish you a Happy New Year. Hope you had fun whatever you got up to:-)
Ha! Thanks! You too! I worked till 11 and then went to bed!
You're a wild man! Well, at least you're makin some money. I've been working like a dog too. Heading to Woodstock on Monday and then NYC. Looking forward to getting away:-)
Hoping for heavy snow. We'll see...
I'm working Brunch bar this Sat. You should come visit me for a Bloody Mary and I'll pay you too for the Zoe walks.
Thanks but I'm gona be out of town, next week though
Ok, I'll be back from NY next Sat, Jan 11th.
